\f1\b0 Using the\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.tvmaze.com/api"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 \strokec3 http://www.tvmaze.com/api}}\'a0create a single page application showing episodes timeline for the selected TV show.\
