\f0\b Time Required:\'a0
\f1\b0 The candidate is not expected to spend more than 6-8 hours on the development.\
\'a0\

\f0\b Functionality:
\f1\b0 \
As the user starts typing the TV show title, a list of suggestions appears based on user input. Suggestions include TV show title, premiere date and a show rating. When the user selects a show from the dropdown list with suggestions, the TV show summary appears and season selection dropdown. As soon as the user selects a season, all episodes from the selected season are placed on a timeline proportionally, based on the show air date. E.g. if episodes were airing every 1st day of the month, they should be distributed evenly. Each episode on the timeline is represented by a dot. An episode number and name is shown under each dot. As the user clicks on the dot, a tooltip appears with the selected episode name, episode image and summary. If no image is available, show \'93image not available\'94 placeholder image. Clear button resets current TV show selection.\'a0\
\'a0\

